fields.fieldText: 6. Provide electrical power to package and record operational settings programmed in controller. Use controller to navigate to the appropriate location and record:

fields.name: Pull_the_antenna_out_of_its_box
fields.fieldText: Pull the antenna out of its box, attach it to the compressor roof and route the wire from the antenna to the iConn modem. A hole should already exist above the control box. Remove plug that is currently in that hole.

fields.name: Connect_the_wire_to_the_modem

fields.name: If_the_customer_does_not_wish_to_activate_the_iConn_system_do_not_install_the_an

fields.name: Eight_Jog_main_motor
fields.fieldText: 8. Jog main motor to verify the compressor rotation is correct. If the rotation is not correct, the motor phase must be changed and repeat jog.

fields.name: Disconnect_lockout_and_tagout_power_supply_to_the_compressor_package

fields.name: Exchange_any_two_phases
fields.fieldText: Exchange any two phases of the incoming power line at the distribution block. Note that this task does not affect the rotation of any VFD-driven device, such as the main motors or the heat exchanger fan motor.
